OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a bright, sunny start,
OL,6,Fcloud will increase from late morning.
OL,7,FShowers developing during the early
OL,8,Fafternoon, clearing into the evening.
OL,9,FBreezy at times, particularly on
OL,10,Fcoasts, where there will be a cooler
OL,11,Ffeel to the day.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy during the evening
OL,14,Fwith clear spells then developing into
OL,15,Fthe night. Largely dry overnight,
OL,16,Faside from isolated coastal showers.
OL,17,FFeeling cool in brisk northerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
