OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FSunny spells for many,
OL,6,Fthough cooler than recent days.
OL,7,FLargely dry to the west, with
OL,8,Foccasional showers affecting East
OL,9,FAnglia. Breezy, especially along
OL,10,Fcoasts. Chilly overnight with frosts
OL,11,Fdeveloping.
OL,12,
OL,13,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,14,FThursday brings sunny spells and the
OL,15,Fodd shower. Conditions turn more
OL,16,Funsettled Friday and Saturday with
OL,17,Fspells of rain or showers,
OL,18,Foccasionally heavy. At times cool,
OL,19,Fwith isolated frosts overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
